reference_patterns: `serde_json::Value` belongs at parser, adapter, or intentionally documented dynamic boundaries; public library APIs expose typed contracts. | HTTP and async service layers translate raw wire payloads into named request and response types before crossing domain boundaries. | Agent edits should not spread untyped JSON shape through public APIs because that forces later agents to infer payload contracts from call-site archaeology.
target_rationale: The fixture is a tiny public API shape check; detecting dynamic JSON boundaries should remain bounded in unit-test scale.
